data.description: Look no further than this beautifully well kept two story home in Lithonia, Ga. Minutes away from Stonecrest Mall and with easy access to I-20, this beauty comes with 3 large sized bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms on the upper level and one spacious half bath on the main level. Hardwood floors greets you at the amazing foyer entrance into the larger than life family room that opens to the kitchen for great family moments. The kitchen has stainless appliances and an eating area for family time. The large master bedroom has double vanity, separate shower and tub combo and tons of closet space. This home has been well kept and renovated to the T. This one won't last long. Come see it ASAP!  Full year home warranty offered with accepted offer!
